      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those who prioritize utility over perfection. The exterior has visible signs of age, including some paint oxidation and minor door dings, while the interior shows typical wear such as light staining on the upholstery and minor scuffs on the dashboard. Mechanically, it runs and drives, though it may benefit from a tune-up and some routine maintenance in the near future. It is a solid, honest car for anyone seeking affordable transportation or a straightforward project.",
